              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="size-6 fill-yellow-400"
            >
              <path
                d="M10.788 3.21c.448-1.077 1.976-1.077 2.424 0l2.082 5.006 5.404.434c1.164.093 1.636 1.545.749 2.305l-4.117 3.527 1.257 5.273c.271 1.136-.964 2.033-1.96 1.425L12 18.354 7.373 21.18c-.996.608-2.231-.29-1.96-1.425l1.257-5.273-4.117-3.527c-.887-.76-.415-2.212.749-2.305l5.404-.434 2.082-5.005Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="size-6 fill-yellow-400"
            >
              <path
                d="M10.788 3.21c.448-1.077 1.976-1.077 2.424 0l2.082 5.006 5.404.434c1.164.093 1.636 1.545.749 2.305l-4.117 3.527 1.257 5.273c.271 1.136-.964 2.033-1.96 1.425L12 18.354 7.373 21.18c-.996.608-2.231-.29-1.96-1.425l1.257-5.273-4.117-3.527c-.887-.76-.415-2.212.749-2.305l5.404-.434 2.082-5.005Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-bold text-base">Rated company</h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-4">
          Our professional Auto Transport Advisors are here 365 days a year and
          will guide you through the shipping process if you choose to buy a new
          car online and have it delivered straight to your door.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-bold mt-8 text-base">
          Track your order on Live Chat
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-4">
          Once you make that big purchase, you can track your car shipping order
          via calling your dedicated agent or ask questions about your order on
          Live Chat!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
      <h2 class="text-4xl text-[#19171fd2] font-medium mb-10">
        Why choose Cayad for your car shipment
      </h2>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img
              src="/img/dollar.webp"
              width="1080" height="1080"
              class="w-24 h-20 mb-2"
              alt="car shipping buyers dollar logo"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">The most cost effective company</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                In order to be the best and ser you always we are decided to be
                the most cost effective solution for all your transportation
                needs nawadays, we have the oportunity to move for you at the
                best price ever.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img
              src="/img/easy.webp"
              width="1080" height="1080"
              class="w-24 h-20 mb-2"
              alt="auto onlyne buyers transport easy logo"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">A+ claims team</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                Antique car haulers carry higher insurance policy limits due to
                the higher value of their cargo. Our compliance team checks the
                insurance coverage of all of our carriers. If your vehicle is
                worth $50,000 or more, we recommend using enclosed auto
                transport.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img
              src="/img/call.webp"
              width="120" height="120"
              class="w-24 h-24 mb-2"
              alt="car shipping online buyers call logo"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">
                Covered auto transport compliance standards
              </h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                We have a compliance department that checks all exotic auto
                transport carriers in our network to ensure we only work with
                the most professional car haulers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/onlinebuyers.webp"
              width="728" height="485"
              class="object-cover rounded-xl w-full h-full"
              alt="car shipping online buyer"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
